<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:08:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加沙战争目标、撤离人员和费城：以色列总理内塔尼亚胡的事实核查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-goals-evacuees-and-philadelphi-fact-checking-israeli-pm-netanyahu/00000191-b7b9-d95b-a1d5-bfbdfd6d0000</link><description>自战争爆发以来，内塔尼亚胡总理就一些关键问题提出了许多主张。然而，仔细观察就会发现，内塔尼亚胡并不像他表面上表现的那么诚实，他在以色列的战争目标、费城路线等问题上反复无常。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 13:52:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-goals-evacuees-and-philadelphi-fact-checking-israeli-pm-netanyahu/00000191-b7b9-d95b-a1d5-bfbdfd6d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列预备役军人袭击为援助组织工作的加沙卡车司机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reservists-assault-gazan-truck-drivers-working-for-aid-organizations/00000191-b71d-d13c-a39b-bf9d24710000</link><description>巴勒斯坦司机接受了以色列安全部门的筛查，与哈马斯或其他恐怖组织没有联系。以色列国防军士兵个人反对援助物资进入加沙地带，他们在凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点加沙一侧殴打、戴上手铐并蒙住他们的眼睛。截至本报告发布，无人受到质疑</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 12:11:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reservists-assault-gazan-truck-drivers-working-for-aid-organizations/00000191-b71d-d13c-a39b-bf9d24710000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和犹太领导人谴责英国暂停向以色列转让部分武器的“可耻”决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-jewish-leaders-slam-u-k-s-shameful-suspension-of-some-arms-sales-to-israel/00000191-b783-d9c6-a997-bfab71610000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡说：“英国的错误决定只会让哈马斯更加嚣张。”英国首席拉比谴责部分武器暂停是“乞丐的信仰”</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 12:07:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-jewish-leaders-slam-u-k-s-shameful-suspension-of-some-arms-sales-to-israel/00000191-b783-d9c6-a997-bfab71610000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列重新占领加沙，“神圣”的费城路线将由人质尸体铺成</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/the-holy-philadelphi-route-will-be-paved-with-hostages-bodies-as-israel-reoccupies-gaza/00000191-b766-d9c6-a997-bf6e0cc30000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡和他的部长们知道，军队在加沙和埃及边境的存在过去并没有阻止哈马斯的袭击。其目标实际上是让以色列永远留在加沙，这个目标不再是愚蠢的，而是邪恶的</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 11:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/the-holy-philadelphi-route-will-be-paved-with-hostages-bodies-as-israel-reoccupies-gaza/00000191-b766-d9c6-a997-bf6e0cc30000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列西岸攻势加剧，简易爆炸物成为主要挑战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/as-israels-west-bank-offensive-intensifies-improvised-explosives-become-major-challenge/00000191-b6c0-dffe-abf9-bfff4a150000</link><description>约旦河西岸北部的大规模行动对巴勒斯坦难民营造成严重破坏，以色列军队努力“剥落”路面以发现埋设的爆炸物</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 09:22:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/as-israels-west-bank-offensive-intensifies-improvised-explosives-become-major-challenge/00000191-b6c0-dffe-abf9-bfff4a150000</guid></item><item><title>以色列侨民部长出访行程曝光：大多与极右翼领导人会面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-diaspora-ministers-travel-itinerary-revealed-mostly-visits-to-far-right-leaders/00000191-b2dd-db99-a1d1-bfffe4700000</link><description>这位侨民部长 2024 年初的旅行计划包括与法国、西班牙和波兰的极右翼政党领导人会面，这些国家与以色列没有正式关系；文件显示，此次旅行花费约 500,000 谢克尔</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 06:51:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-diaspora-ministers-travel-itinerary-revealed-mostly-visits-to-far-right-leaders/00000191-b2dd-db99-a1d1-bfffe4700000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯在被谋杀几天后播放了以色列人质伊登·耶鲁沙米在加沙被囚禁的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/hamas-airs-video-of-israeli-hostage-eden-yerushalmi-in-gaza-captivity-days-after-murder/00000191-b67f-d9c6-a997-be7f05b10000</link><description>24 岁的 Yerushalmi 来自特拉维夫，于 10 月 7 日在 Nova 狂欢节上被绑架。预计她将在协议的最初人道主义阶段获释，本周早些时候，她的尸体与其他五名人质一起被归还</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 06:27:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/hamas-airs-video-of-israeli-hostage-eden-yerushalmi-in-gaza-captivity-days-after-murder/00000191-b67f-d9c6-a997-be7f05b10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员：10月7日不启动调查可能会导致国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡、Gallant发出逮捕令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officials-refusal-to-appoint-oct-7-inquiry-increases-risk-of-icc-arrest-warrants/00000191-b5aa-dc3b-a7df-f7fabd4e0000</link><description>司法部消息人士称，政府拒绝总检察长关于成立国家调查委员会的建议，增加了检方请求获得批准的可能性。与此同时，以色列也得到了多个国家、组织和学术界对其立场的支持。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 03:01:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officials-refusal-to-appoint-oct-7-inquiry-increases-risk-of-icc-arrest-warrants/00000191-b5aa-dc3b-a7df-f7fabd4e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列怒火中烧，内塔尼亚胡编造谎言并判处人质死刑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-gaza-map-failed-to-show-the-route-he-used-to-funnel-qatari-cash-to-hamas/00000191-b46f-dc3b-a7df-f77f9c820000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡以安全担忧来掩盖自己的动机，主要是为了保护自己的政治地位。他正在努力维持他的联盟，如果加沙协议获得通过，这个联盟可能会瓦解</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 03:00:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-gaza-map-failed-to-show-the-route-he-used-to-funnel-qatari-cash-to-hamas/00000191-b46f-dc3b-a7df-f77f9c820000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人称，以色列国防军在西岸开火，导致一名 16 岁少年丧生；黎巴嫩火箭弹袭击以色列北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article-live/netanyahu-nixes-key-part-of-u-s-led-gaza-plan-hamas-releases-video-of-murdered-hostage/00000191-b5c7-dd1b-a7db-b7df5fc60000</link><description>消息人士告诉美国有线电视新闻网，内塔尼亚胡承诺永远不会让费城“鱼雷”人质谈判被破坏 ■ 内塔尼亚胡否决了美国领导的加沙计划的关键部分；哈马斯发布被谋杀人质的视频 ■ 欧洲汉莎航空集团航空公司恢复飞往特拉维夫的航班</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 02:55:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article-live/netanyahu-nixes-key-part-of-u-s-led-gaza-plan-hamas-releases-video-of-murdered-hostage/00000191-b5c7-dd1b-a7db-b7df5fc60000</guid></item><item><title>新纪录片将曝光内塔尼亚胡腐败审讯的前所未见的镜头</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/u-s-documentary-to-show-unseen-leaked-footage-of-netanyahus-police-interrogation/00000191-b4bf-dc3b-a7df-f7ff167e0000</link><description>制片人亚历克斯·吉布尼表示，《比比档案》将于下周在多伦多电影节首映，并提供“其贪污腐败性格的有力证据”</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 22:14:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/u-s-documentary-to-show-unseen-leaked-footage-of-netanyahus-police-interrogation/00000191-b4bf-dc3b-a7df-f7ff167e0000</guid></item><item><title>法官释放18名停火抗议者；以色列警方称“一定程度”要求对他们进行审判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/judge-releases-18-tel-aviv-protesters-police-say-certain-levels-demand-they-be-tried/00000191-b461-dc3b-a7df-f771f4d30000</link><description>一名警方代表承认，大规模人质抗议活动被认为“非常具有侵略性”。法官注意到对被拘留者不利的证据很少，其中一人没有出示任何证据</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 20:24:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/judge-releases-18-tel-aviv-protesters-police-say-certain-levels-demand-they-be-tried/00000191-b461-dc3b-a7df-f771f4d30000</guid></item><item><title>“我们不会停止”：数万名以色列人在愤怒的第三天抗议人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/were-not-stopping-tens-of-thousands-demand-hostage-deal-on-third-day-of-rage-protests/00000191-b403-d95b-a1d5-bd3f47760000</link><description>在特拉维夫、耶路撒冷和其他城市，以色列人周一继续要求达成人质协议和停火。警方与内塔尼亚胡耶路撒冷住所外的抗议者发生冲突，强行逮捕了几名抗议者</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 19:50:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/were-not-stopping-tens-of-thousands-demand-hostage-deal-on-third-day-of-rage-protests/00000191-b403-d95b-a1d5-bd3f47760000</guid></item><item><title>赫什的家人值得拜登、哈里斯和特朗普的思念和祈祷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-02/ty-article/.highlight/hershs-family-deserves-more-than-thoughts-and-prayers-from-biden-harris-and-trump/00000191-b390-dc3b-a7df-f3d050700000</link><description>如果美国立法者和官员真的想向赫什·戈德堡-波林、乔恩和雷切尔致敬，他们就必须公开呼吁达成一项能够确保赫什活着回家的协议</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 17:37:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-02/ty-article/.highlight/hershs-family-deserves-more-than-thoughts-and-prayers-from-biden-harris-and-trump/00000191-b390-dc3b-a7df-f3d050700000</guid></item><item><title>“我们让你失望了”：数千人聚集埋葬被哈马斯谋杀的以色列裔美国人质赫什·戈德堡-波林</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/thousands-gather-to-bury-hersh-goldberg-polin-israeli-american-hostage-killed-by-hamas/00000191-b333-db99-a1d1-bf7fb99e0000</link><description>赫什·戈德堡-波林和其他五名人质在加沙被哈马斯囚禁期间被处决。在他的葬礼上，以色列总统艾萨克·赫尔佐格说：“我想说，我们没能把他带回家，我感到非常遗憾”</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 17:34:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/thousands-gather-to-bury-hersh-goldberg-polin-israeli-american-hostage-killed-by-hamas/00000191-b333-db99-a1d1-bf7fb99e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第332天：拜登称内塔尼亚胡在确保人质协议方面做得不够</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-332-netanyahu-not-doing-enough-to-secure-hostage-deal-biden-says/00000191-b3bf-dd1b-a7db-b7ff81db0001</link><description>据报道，美国正在制定最终的“接受或放弃”停火提案 ■ 本-格维尔表示，他“并不羞于说”，他正在利用自己在政府中的权力“阻止一项鲁莽的协议，并完全停止任何谈判” ■ 数千人全国各地的以色列人抗议支持人质协议 ■ 英国宣布暂停向以色列运送一系列武器 ■ 战争进入 332 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 17:24:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-332-netanyahu-not-doing-enough-to-secure-hostage-deal-biden-says/00000191-b3bf-dd1b-a7db-b7ff81db0001</guid></item><item><title>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡，邪恶的救世主，领导着谎言和死亡的邪教</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/benjamin-netanyahu-the-vile-messiah-leading-a-cult-of-lies-and-death/00000191-b286-d93f-a5bb-b3967ae70000</link><description>尽管总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡（Benjamin Netanyahu）主持了许多失败 — — 包括伊朗、经济、生活成本和 10 月 7 日 — — 但仍然受到超过四分之一的以色列人的崇拜。他的失败和他的支持之间的差距具有邪教的所有特征</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 17:16:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/benjamin-netanyahu-the-vile-messiah-leading-a-cult-of-lies-and-death/00000191-b286-d93f-a5bb-b3967ae70000</guid></item><item><title>被以色列杀害后，这位年轻的 TikToker 成为加沙迷失一代的象征</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/after-being-killed-by-israel-young-tiktoker-becomes-a-symbol-of-gazas-lost-generation/00000191-b359-dc3b-a7df-f35928e90000</link><description>19 岁的梅多·哈利米 (Medo Halimy) 凭借讲述加沙日常生活的乐观视频在网上走红。上周，他在一家临时咖啡馆上网时被杀</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 17:03:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/after-being-killed-by-israel-young-tiktoker-becomes-a-symbol-of-gazas-lost-generation/00000191-b359-dc3b-a7df-f35928e90000</guid></item><item><title>英国暂停向以色列出售部分武器，理由是加沙存在违反国际法的“明显风险”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/u-k-suspends-some-arms-sales-to-israel-citing-clear-risk-of-intl-law-breach-in-gaza/00000191-b38e-dc3b-a7df-f3def2160000</link><description>这是自加沙冲突开始以来西方政府采取的最严厉行动之一，可能会鼓励其他国家采取类似措施</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 16:39:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/u-k-suspends-some-arms-sales-to-israel-citing-clear-risk-of-intl-law-breach-in-gaza/00000191-b38e-dc3b-a7df-f3def2160000</guid></item><item><title>以色列阿拉伯社区向加沙捐赠数十吨援助物资，但以色列阻止其进入</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-arab-community-donated-dozens-of-tons-of-aid-to-gaza-but-israel-blocks-its-entry/00000191-a8a6-d3dd-a991-a8be2e7d0000</link><description>以色列阿拉伯社区的一位领导人表示，“没有理由长期储存这些捐款，因为有些可能会变质”，因为以色列军队声称这些捐款不符合进入加沙的条件</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 14:10:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-arab-community-donated-dozens-of-tons-of-aid-to-gaza-but-israel-blocks-its-entry/00000191-a8a6-d3dd-a991-a8be2e7d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>